==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Washoe process
<hw>Wash"oe proc`ess</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[From the
<etsep>Washoe</etsep> district, Nevada.]</ety> <def>The process of
treating silver ores by grinding in pans or tubs with the addition of
mercury, and sometimes of chemicals such as blue vitriol and
salt.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wash-off</ent>⟦br⟧
